posting_body: ['San Francisco - Golden Gate Heights - Apartment for rent', 'Golden Gate Heights 3bed/2bat', 'Flat w/Garage Parking', 'Link to mobile layout: \xa0 <URL>', 'Summary:', 'Rent: $4650', 'Bed / Bath: 3 / 2', 'Type: Apartment', 'Term: 12 Months', 'Please contact:', 'Chuck Totah \xa0 |', 'show contact info', '| \xa0 \xa0 <URL>', 'Description:', 'Bright and spacious, ~1,200 sq ft 3 bed, 2 full baths, top floor unit with serene hillside and Golden Gate views!', "Great Central Location: only a few blocks to N-Judah Muni line, Golden Gate Park, UCSF and Inner-Sunset's shops and cafes.", 'Features Include', '~ Remodeled kitchen with granite counter-tops, newer cabinets with tons of storage space, and new appliances including dishwasher and garbage disposal', '~ Large open living room with functional wood burning fireplace and separate dining area', '~ Washer and dryer in building', '~ One reserved garage parking', '~ Large backyard with gardening areas', '~ Pets considered (restrictions apply)', 'This is a non-smoking unit.', 'Service or support animals which are necessary due to disability will be allowed.', 'Details:', 'Floors: Hardwood', 'Kitchen: Remodeled', 'Laundry:', 'In Building', 'Outside area: Shared Yard', 'Parking: Garage', 'Parking Fee: $0', 'Pets:   Cat,    Dog    OK', 'View: Hillside', 'Location:', 'Funston Avenue & Moraga St, San Francisco, California', 'Meet the J.Wavro Team:', '<URL>', 'Please contact:', 'Chuck Totah \xa0 |', 'show contact info', '| \xa0 \xa0 <URL>', 'Preview more properties at <URL>', 'This unit is a rental unit subject to the San Francisco Rent Ordinance, which limits evictions without just cause, and which states that any waiver by a tenant of their rights under the Rent Ordinance is void as contrary to public policy.', 'Content and Images © 2003 - 2021 J.Wavro \xa0 | \xa0 BRE # 01810008 \xa0 | \xa0 cl31397592014895-0']
